        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nNot sure that sp-partner was intended to store the credentials. There is another commit coming that defines the external ONAP with relationship to esr-system-info. The commit that is coming soon agrees with you.\n\nWill ask the developers about the \"callsource\" property.\n\nsp-partner did not seem like a \"network\" object to me, so best guess is \"business\" fits, unless a better suggestion is made.",
